3520  foreach (float f in weights)
3521  {
3522  totalWeight += f;
3523  }
3524

3526  float total = totalWeight + baseWeight;

3530  {

3534  UnsafeBuffer buf = p._faceData[x + 2];

3560

3562  }
3563

3566  }
3567  }

3573  }
